# ── TechJobs Hub — API Keys ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# 1. Adzuna (FREE — 250 requests/month free tier)
#    Sign up at: https://developer.adzuna.com/
ADZUNA_APP_ID=your_adzuna_app_id_here
ADZUNA_APP_KEY=your_adzuna_app_key_here

# 2. JSearch via RapidAPI (FREE — 200 requests/month free tier)
#    Sign up at: https://rapidapi.com/letscrape-6bRBa3QguO5/api/jsearch
JSEARCH_KEY=your_rapidapi_key_here

# 3. RemoteOK — NO KEY NEEDED (completely free public API)

# ── Notes ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Without keys → app still works with curated sample jobs (15 real listings)
# With Adzuna + JSearch → 40-100 real live jobs per search
# RemoteOK always active → 25 remote-only tech jobs always included
